                  <div itemprop="description" class="element-hidden">GUEST POST: The Founder and Creative Director of More Love Letters riffs on how hand-written letters can change people&#039;s lives, and why letters continue to matter even in an age of digital communication. </div>
                <header class="article-header">
          <div class="group-article-meta">
            <div
  class="field field-name-post-date"
  itemprop="datePublished"
  content="2013-12-07"
>
  December 7, 2013  <span class="separator">|</span> </div>
            <div class="field article-author-top" itemscope itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
  <span class="label">By </span>
